SetEnv icons $[HOME]/.fvwm/icons

DestroyDecor xo
AddToDecor xo
+ TitleStyle Centered Height 52 -- Flat
+ ButtonStyle Reset
+ ButtonStyle All -- Flat
+ ButtonStyle All -- UseTitleStyle
+ AddButtonStyle All Vector 2 1x1@4 1x1@4
+ AddButtonStyle 1 \
 	ActiveUp (Pixmap $[icons]/x_new.png -- Flat) \
 	ActiveDown (Pixmap $[icons]/x_new.png -- Flat) \
 	Inactive (Pixmap $[icons]/x_new.png -- Flat)
+ AddButtonStyle 3 \
 	ActiveUp (Pixmap $[icons]/o_new.png -- Flat) \
 	ActiveDown (Pixmap $[icons]/o_new.png -- Flat) \
 	Inactive (Pixmap $[icons]/o_new.png -- Flat)

Mouse 1 1 A Close
Mouse 1 3 A Maximize

Style "*" UseDecor xo
Style "*" TitleAtBottom
Style "*" BorderWidth 0, HandleWidth 0

DesktopSize 1x1
